<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l30">etlich die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> / <expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / . <expan>Laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr vveiſheit vviſſen / daʒ der <expan>weiſſemburg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l31">nicht mer etc . vt <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Nothaft / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>An<ex>te</ex></expan> Oſwaldȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_241" id="119r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
